Type: Package
Package: lobsteR
Title: Access and Process LOBSTER high-frequency data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Karol", "Kulma", , "kulmakarol@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
    person("Stefan", "Voigt", , "stefan.voigt@econ.ku.dk", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
  )
Description: Provides tools to authenticate with lobsterdata.com, request,
    download, and unzip high-frequency financial market data. The package
    streamlines the workflow from data request to analysis-ready datasets,
    with built-in functions for unzipping and cleaning LOBSTER data files.
    For advanced high-frequency econometric analysis, see the
    'highfrequency' package.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/voigtstefan/lobster
BugReports: https://github.com/voigtstefan/lobster/issues
